## 3. Module Hierarchy
- [index.html](file:///c:/Users/User/Documents/MyProjects/exam-dashboard/index.html): Main dashboard entry (loads `app.js`).
- [analytics.html](file:///c:/Users/User/Documents/MyProjects/exam-dashboard/analytics.html): Insights Hub (loads `analytics_app.js`).
- [src/storage.js](file:///c:/Users/User/Documents/MyProjects/exam-dashboard/src/storage.js): The source of truth for all data interactions.
- [src/ai_service.js](file:///c:/Users/User/Documents/MyProjects/exam-dashboard/src/ai_service.js): Handles agentic calls to Gemini.
- [src/api_modal_manager.js](file:///c:/Users/User/Documents/MyProjects/exam-dashboard/src/api_modal_manager.js): Shared logic for API key management across pages.
